title: S9 E5: Fabricated
description:
Kenji recruited a friend to help investigate Ardie, reporting his findings to Darcy in hopes she would see the truth. Despite her own Ardie induced trauma, Darcy dug in deeper. As Kenji’s investigation intensified, Ardie lashed out with legal action, threats, and violence. Distraught and looking for more answers about Ardie’s true identity, Kenji found more than he bargained for.
